NaemonBox Version 0.0.7-RCx
==============================================================================

Version 0.0.7-RC6
=============

   * Webmin 1.780 (issue #25)
   * nagios-business-process-addon-0.9.6
   * naemonbox --backup|--checknagios|--definenetwork|--purge|--reboot|--restart|--searcherrors|--searchlogs|--status|--start|--stop|--version
   * purgeip.sh when your server change IP address, use this script to set all your conf files with the new IP address 

Version 0.0.7-RC5
=============

Bugs corrected :

   * WebUI : Failed to connect to the database: SQLSTATE[28000] [1045] Access denied for user 'root'@'localhost' (using password: YES). (issue #22]

Version 0.0.7-RC4
=============

Bugs corrected :

   * Thruk Addons & Plugin Manager Readonly: Make sure the config file is writable New Web UI based on bootstrap (issue #21)
   * Cannot commit changes Thruk Business process ( # 20)

   
Version 0.0.7-RC3
=============  

Enhancements and new features:

   * Layout of the wiki home page (issue #19)

Bugs corrected : 
 
   * Panorama view doesnt work in version Thruk 1.88-2 (issue #18)  
   * Possible precedence issue with control flow operator (issue #17) 

   
Version 0.0.7-RC2
=============    

Bugs corrected :

   * Fix motd error on apache (issue #16)

 Enhancements and new features:
 
   * New Web UI based on bootstrap
   
Version 0.0.7-RC1
============= 

   * Add 3 new graph template to Cacti (XML) (issue #15)
   * Add 8 more contrib logos for naemon classic themes (issue #14)
   * Add 653 more contrib plugins (issue #13)
   * Upgrading installs to the new operating system Debian 8.1 JESSIE (issue #12)
   * Naemon configuration pack for VMWare (issue #11)
 
 Update :
 
   * Naemon 1.0.3
   * Nagvis 1.8.5
   * Webmin 1.760_all 
 
 Enhancements and new features:
 
   * nmap2naemon 0.1.4 (discovery module)
 
